;IN THIS MUTANT STRUCTURE THE SIDE CHAIN OF GLU 16 APPEARS
TO HAVE TWO DIFFERENT CONFORMATIONS.  THE STRUCTURE WAS
REFINED WITH THE SIDE CHAIN IN THE TWO ALTERNATIVE
CONFORMATIONS.  PROTEIN DATA BANK ENTRIES 1L42 AND 1L43
CONTAIN COORDINATES CORRESPONDING TO THE TWO DIFFERENT
CONFORMATIONS OF GLU 16.
;
